Package org.turbogwt.ext.gwtp.databind.client

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    BindingUiHandlers
    Use this interface on classes that implement the controls required by a BindingView to communicate back with its PresenterWidget.
    BindingView<H extends BindingUiHandlers>
    The interface for view classes that handles all the UI-related code for a Presenter supporting Databind.
    PopupBindingView<H extends BindingUiHandlers>
    The interface for View classes that is meant to be displayed as a popup supporting Databind.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BindingViewImpl<H extends BindingUiHandlers>
    Base class for a BindingView.
    PopupBindingViewImpl<H extends BindingUiHandlers>
    Base class for a PopupBindingView.
